                                            </TextBlock>
                                            <TextBlock FontSize="20" Margin="0,10,0,0">
                                                <Span Foreground="#FF91711B" FontFamily="Fonts/#Interstate-Bold">BRONZE:</Span> <Span Foreground="#FFB2E7E3">9415 coins</Span>
